name: "BBC World News"
year: 2013
image: "/assets/images/team/christina.gif"
---

We developed a strategic vision for the nascent BBC Trending brand, trained the staff on social-first programming, and reconfigured existing talent and resources into a new workflow. We also launched the BBC News Instagram account by reimagining BBC's newly retired Ceefax program as a video and photo format custom-tailored for the platform.
